	directAnswerHtml={`<strong style="color: var(--color-ink);">If you are a Muslim with a sincere heart toward God, this page is offered to you in respect and love.</strong> You know the discipline of prayer, the hunger to please God, the reverence for the One who is supremely great and merciful — Ar-Rahman, Ar-Rahim. The <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Father's Heart Bible™</a> is a fresh English translation you can read and <em>listen to</em> free — and it reveals God not only as Creator and Master, but as a <em>Father</em> wherever Scripture reveals Him as Father. Whether you have searched "does God love me," "is God a Father," "Bible verses about God's love," or "who is God in the Bible" — you are welcome here to consider, gently and without pressure, the One who calls you not servant, but beloved child.`}
