	painsHeading={`Seeking the nearness of God`}
	painsIntroHtml={`Across the world, more than a billion and a half people order their days around the worship of God — a devotion that is sincere, disciplined, and deeply felt. The numbers tell the story of a vast hunger for the divine.`}
